data.description: Opportunity awaits you in this special single story home with pool and spa located on a corner lot in northwest Las Vegas. Well maintained home with lots of special touches created by the homeowners. Gorgeous wood like floors throughout. Recently painted interior. Open floor plan creates a sense of space with lots of natural light. Ceiling fans with lights in Great Room and Primary Bedroom. Roomy primary bedroom. Primary bathroom includes walk-in shower, double sink and large walk-in closet. Recessed Can lighting in bedrooms and Great Room. Covered patio retreat next to refreshing pool with spa. Garage with storage cabinets. Low maintenance backyard with synthetic grass. Welcome Home!
